<section>
  <h3>Lacanche Appliances We Repair</h3>

  <h4>Lacanche Range and Range Cooker Repair</h4>
  <p>
    We repair Lacanche gas and dual-fuel ranges and range cookers. Common problems include burner ignition failure, weak or uneven flame, temperature inconsistency, oven not heating properly, broiler issues, and control or switch malfunctions.
  </p>

  <h4>Lacanche Oven Repair</h4>
  <p>
    We service Lacanche ovens with problems such as uneven cooking temperatures, heating element issues, thermostat faults, fan problems, broiler failures, and timer or control issues.
  </p>

  <h4>Lacanche Rangetop, Burner, French Top, and Griddle Repair</h4>
  <p>
    We repair Lacanche cooking surfaces with ignition problems, unstable flame, slow heat response, damaged burner components, control issues, and performance problems affecting French tops, griddles, and planchas.
  </p>

  <h4>Lacanche Hood Repair</h4>
  <p>
    We diagnose and repair Lacanche hoods with fan motor issues, poor airflow, lighting problems, switch failures, and control malfunctions.
  </p>

  <h4>Lacanche Control and Hardware Issues</h4>
  <p>
    We also inspect and repair control knobs, switches, timers, indicators, hinges, gaskets, and alignment issues that affect the performance and usability of Lacanche appliances.
  </p>
</section>

