    <li>Lacanche oven not heating evenly</li>
    <li>Lacanche range not reaching the correct temperature</li>
    <li>Lacanche burner flame too low or uneven</li>
    <li>Lacanche hood fan not pulling air properly</li>
    <li>Lacanche control knob, switch, or timer issues</li>
    <li>Lacanche French top or griddle not heating correctly</li>
